Class NullPreProcessor

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.marcolotz.imageprocess.ImageProcessingClass
      • com.marcolotz.imageprocess.NullPreProcessor

  • public class NullPreProcessor
extends ImageProcessingClass
    This class basically return its input value. It is used as a wildcard in order to keep the modularity of the code. If an user in the future desires to produce a preprocess module, it can be easily applied as a plug-in.
